overview:
Qubed advertising is created to provide outstanding advertising and marketing services to clients globally. We are experienced in the areas of graphic design, printing services, website design and advertising. We work towards providing complete satisfaction to our customers. We have a long list of happy clients who keep coming back to us for all their advertising needs.

Our company was founded and is headed by Miklos Oszkar. Mr. Oszkar is a pioneer in the advertising arena and has lead several successful advertising assignments for prestigious institutions. He now wants to expand his service offerings worldwide and has come up with Qubed. Qubed advertising is a Romania based company that has a good reserve of innovative and fresh talents. Our team is highly creative and follows an out of the box thinking approach. In order to stand out among the highly competitive business sphere, you need to have a cutting edge over your competitors which can be obtained only through effective advertising. We guarantee to provide you with complete professional advertising services that help you gain an eminent position in the global market.
